Was für ein Finale der FIFA WM 2022! An Dramatik kaum zu überbieten. Argentinien geht durch Lionel Messi und Angel di Maria in der ersten Halbzeit mit 2:0 in Führung. In der zweiten Hälfte kann  Kylian Mbappe dank eines Blitzschlags innerhalb von 94 Sekunden spät ausgleichen. In der Verlängerung ist es dann Lionel Messi, der zunächst den Unterschied macht. Doch Kylian Mbappe kann erneut durch einen Elfmeter-Treffer kontern. Das Spiel geht ins Elfmeterschießen, in dem Argentinien die besseren Nerven hat. Lionel Messi macht sich mit seinem ersten WM-Titel unsterblich!

 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The host, Kapil Sharma makes a rocking entry to the stage and welcomes everyone to the show. He then proceeds to welcome the special guests for the night. They are none other than the star cast of the upcoming comedy film, Cirkus, starring Ranveer Singh, Jacqueline Fernandez, Pooja Hegde, and Varun Sharma. They are here to promote their film along with their director, Rohit Shetty who tells that the lead character was inspired by Ranveer's real-life personality and energy. To witness more, watch the episode now.

Credits:
Directed by Pradeep Varma
Written by Pradeep Varma
Starring Sree Vishnu & Kayadu Lohar
Cinematography Raj Thota
Edited by Dharmendra Kakarala
Music by Harshavardhan Rameshwar

Synopsis
The film starts on a promising note, with all the departments coming together well, especially Sri Vishnu’s characterisation as a young police officer. Despite solid performances, the film goes downhill after the interval with more conflicts to resolve, routine setting in; and its overarching timeline is its nemesis. Watch it for its first half and if you like lengthy police sagas.
(Follows a sincere police officer and his journey through various phases of his life.)

snippet.title: 💪C'mon! Learn How To Give CPR and Save Life - By Kishor Singh #shorts
snippet.description:
#shorts

For "HUGE" Discount on 3D Animation Course, Call: +91-99830-83303 or Click here 👉🏻 https://professorofhow.com

C'mon! Learn How To Give CPR and Save Life - By Kishor Singh #shorts 

Heart attack is getting more common with time. Double-tap the screen and let's learn how to provide CPR if someone collapsed around you.
A sudden collapse happens during a heart attack. Your heart, which was supplying the oxygenated blood to your organs, will become unable to pump the blood anymore and the organs will start to die because of the deficiency of blood. Your heart is made to pump artificially in this situation so that your organs keep receiving blood until some medical help arrives.
In order to provide CPR, both the hands of the CPR provider should be placed at the lower middle part of the chest. The press should be hard enough to push the chest by 2 inches, and this pushing process should be fast enough to provide more than 100 compressions per minute. These compressions make the heart pump and the organs start to receive the blood.
If these compressions came out to be not so hard or fast enough, the body organs and especially the brain will not receive the blood and start to die within a few seconds.
After 30 compressions, mouth-to-mouth breathing should be given twice, and both of these steps should be repeated until the person gets some medical help or gets normal.
If you are also interested in making these kinds of informative 3D videos, hit the link given in the pinned comment.

snippet.title: इन्जिनियर सागर ढकालको यक्ष प्रश्न- काङ्ग्रेसमा राणा शासन,जनता काकाकुल ?
snippet.description:
- इन्जिनियर सागर ढकालको यक्ष प्रश्न- काङ्ग्रेसमा राणा शासन,जनता काकाकुल ?

यक्ष प्रश्न हिमालय टेलिभिजनबाट हरेक आइतबार र बुधबार राति ९ बजे प्रसारण हुने र समसामयिक विषयका बारेमा उक्त विषयमा विशेष दख्खल राख्ने व्यक्तित्वसँग गरिने टेलिभिजन अन्तर्वार्ता हो। कार्यक्रम प्रस्तोता राजेन्द्र बानियाँ लोकप्रिय टिभी जर्नालिस्ट हुनुहुन्छ।

कार्यक्रम यक्ष प्रश्नको २१०  औं एपिसोडमा  सागर ढकालसंगको यो विशेष कुराकानी ।

Yaksha Prashna with #RajendraBaniya in conversation with Sagar Dhakal 
Presenter: Rajendra Baniya
Guest: Sagar Dhakal 
#RajendraBaniya #sagardhakal #YakshaPrashna  #election2022  
About us

snippet.title: Magne Buda as सुकुम्बासी | Kedar Prasad Ghimire | Sukumbasi | Nepali Movie Scene
snippet.description:
Magne Buda as सुकुम्बासी | Kedar Prasad Ghimire | Sukumbasi | Nepali Movie Scene

Movie: CHHA EKAN CHHA
Director: Dinesh D.C
Producer: Deepakraj Giri, Dipashree Nirula , Niramal Sharma
Story: Deepakraj Giri
Cast: Neeta Dhungana, Deepakraj Giri, Kiran KC, Jitu Nepal, Kedar Ghimire, Sandip Chhetri, Shivahari Paudel

Nepali movie ‘Chha Ekan Chha’ is a comedy film by the well known comedy actors of television. The lead actors in the movie are the well known comedy actors of ‘Tito Satya’, ‘Meri Bassai’ and ‘Jire Khursani’. The movie is produced by the makers of ‘Tito Satya’ – Deepak Raj Giri, Deepa Shree Niraula and Nirmal Sharma (Gaida). The film is directed by Dinesh DC. The lead actress of the movie, Neeta Dhungana, is considered an actress with a lot of potential in the Nepali film industry.

निर्देशक - अजीत  कुमार शर्मा
संगीतकार -  अनुज तिवारी

कथा- पटकथा - चिराग पारेख
संवाद - विरेन्द्र पाशवान 
संकलन - भावीन भुवा

कोरियोग्राफर - दिलीप मिस्त्री
निर्माता – संदीप सिंह , चिराग पारेख ,अजीत कुमार
म्यूजिक,सॅटॅलाइट और डिजिटल पार्टनर - B4U भोजपुरी

B4U टीम- मारुदा शर्मा, नेहा उपाध्या, विशाल यादव
